name: Amrit Mahotsav: Ek Unmukt Yatra (Walk Event, Female)
description:
Hello all,

Hello all,
The Adventure Sports Club of IIT Kanpur brings to you Amritmahotsav: Ek Unmukt Yatra, an event covered under the Government of India initiative, Azadi ka Amrit Mahotsav to commemorate 75 years of independence of India.

It is a run or walk event, where each participant will be expected to cover a distance of 75 km through walking over 18 days. The event starts on 29th July.

This  club is only for the walking female participants

Please join the below Whatsapp group for getting updates on the event.
